      • integrate_risch_rec

        public static Expr[][] integrate_risch_rec(Expr p,
                                           Expr q,
                                           DExtension[] ext)
        Recursive procedure for integrating transcendental elementary functions
        Parameters:
        p - - a multivariate polynomial in Q[ext]
        q - - a multivariate polynomial in Q[ext]
        ext - - a list of differential extensions [t1, ..., tn]
        Returns:
        the list [[v_0], [c_1, v_1], ..., [c_k, v_k]] such that
        integral p/q = v_0 + c_1 log(v_1) + ... + c_k log(v_k)
        or null if there doesn't exist any elementary integral
